<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Wrong Path | The Veil’s Whisper</title>
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #070707;
      color: #c9c9c9;
      font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      height: 100vh;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 2rem;
      background-image: radial-gradient(circle at center, #111 0%, #000 100%);
      animation: fadeIn 2s ease-in;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      color: #a11919;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      animation: pulse 4s infinite;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      max-width: 680px;
      margin: 0 auto 1.4rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    a {
      color: #9c4dfc;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-bottom: 1px dashed #9c4dfc;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    a:hover {
      color: #fff;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #fff;
    }

    .signature {
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
      font-style: italic;
      color: #666;
    }

    .fade {
      opacity: 0.5;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      color: #444;
    }

    .line {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(10px);
      animation: appear 1.5s ease forwards;
    }

    .line:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
    .line:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 1s; }
    .line:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 1.5s; }

    @keyframes pulse {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
      50% { opacity: 0.5; }
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      0% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
      100% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    @keyframes appear {
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Turn Back</h1>

  <div class="line">
    <p>The knowledge you seek is forbidden.<br>You should not have found this place.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="line">
    <p>I felt your presence when you strayed.<br>The Veil shuddered. The dead stirred.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="line">
    <p>If you value your flesh, <a href="/">return now</a>,<br>for this path belongs to me.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="signature">— Nerull, God of Death</div>
  <div class="fade">“You were not invited. You are not forgotten. You are merely next. Prepare to die.”</div>
</body>
</html>
